title: DJ Sona
body:
WD on Concussive and Ethereal.

Typical on Kinetshit. 

Im sick to death of the same old beat and build up of every mainstream "electronic" song now adays, {{summoner:3}} i thought Dada of all people would not have contributed to such crap. Bassnecter on the other hand, still bringing a different bassline everytime, always good vibes. {{summoner:14}} 

/notevenwhingewhinge
